defs.docs:
Small vectors in various sizes. These store a certain number of elements inline and fall back
 to the heap for larger allocations.

defs.name: VecLike

[T]> + ops::IndexMut<ops::RangeFrom<usize>> + ops::Index<ops::RangeTo<usize>,
Output = [T]> + ops::IndexMut<ops::RangeTo<usize>> +
ops::Index<ops::RangeFull, Output = [T]> + ops::IndexMut<ops::RangeFull> +
ops::Deref + ops::DerefMut + Extend<T>
